INFO  2024-06-19 10:33:17,066 [45   ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (400ms) [Parameters=[@__ef_filter__p_0='?' (DbType = Boolean), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AddressId], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DateOfBirth], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[EmailAddress], [t].[FirstName], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[LastName], [t].[MobileNumber], [t0].[Id], [t0].[City], [t0].[Country], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[PostalCode], [t0].[StreeAddress]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AddressId], [p].[CreationTime], [p].[CreatorUserId], [p].[DateOfBirth], [p].[DeleterUserId], [p].[DeletionTime], [p].[EmailAddress], [p].[FirstName], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[LastModificationTime], [p].[LastModifierUserId], [p].[LastName], [p].[MobileNumber]
    FROM [Persons] AS [p]
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ORDER BY [p].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[PersonId] = [t0].[Id]

) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[PersonId] = [t0].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AddressId], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DateOfBirth], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[EmailAddress], [t].[FirstName], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[LastName], [t].[MobileNumber], [t0].[Id], [t0].[City], [t0].[Country], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[PostalCode], [t0].[StreeAddress]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AddressId], [p].[CreationTime], [p].[CreatorUserId], [p].[DateOfBirth], [p].[DeleterUserId], [p].[DeletionTime], [p].[EmailAddress], [p].[FirstName], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[LastModificationTime], [p].[LastModifierUserId], [p].[LastName], [p].[MobileNumber]

    FROM [Skills] AS [s]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id]
        FROM [Persons] AS [p]
        WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
    ) AS [t] ON [s].[PersonId] = [t].[Id]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit) OR [s].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND [t].[Id] = @__input_PersonId_0
    ORDER BY [s].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]

ORDER BY [a].[Priority] DESC, [a].[TryCount], [a].[NextTryTime]
